name: Mediterranean Pinwheels
description: Flaky puff pastry rolled with a filling of hummus, spinach, roasted red peppers, feta cheese, and sun-dried tomatoes. A perfect bite-sized Mediterranean treat.

name: Fried Wonton
description: Crispy fried wonton wrappers filled with a seasoned mix of pork, shrimp, garlic, and green onions. Served with a sweet chili dipping sauce.

name: Buffalo Chicken Taquitos
description: Spicy shredded buffalo chicken wrapped in a crispy tortilla, filled with cream cheese, cheddar, and green onions. Served with ranch dipping sauce.

name: Asparagus Pastry Bundle
description: Tender asparagus spears wrapped in buttery puff pastry, baked to perfection with a sprinkle of parmesan cheese and black pepper.

name: Smash Burger with Chips
description: Juicy smashed beef patty topped with melted cheddar, lettuce, tomato, and pickles. Served on a toasted bun with a side of crispy chips.

name: Beef Stew
description: Hearty beef stew slow-cooked with tender chunks of beef, carrots, potatoes, onions, and peas, all simmered in a rich gravy.

name: Lasagna
description: Layers of lasagna noodles, ricotta cheese, ground beef, marinara sauce, and mozzarella, baked to a golden, cheesy perfection.

name: Grilled Cheeseburger Wraps
description: Grilled flour tortillas stuffed with ground beef, cheddar cheese, lettuce, tomatoes, and pickles. A portable cheeseburger experience!

name: Sâ€™mores Pizza
description: A dessert pizza with a graham cracker crust, melted chocolate, and toasted marshmallows. A fun twist on the classic campfire treat.

name: Oreo Cheesecake
description: Creamy cheesecake filled with crushed Oreo cookies and topped with a chocolate drizzle and more Oreos for the perfect cookie lover's dessert.

name: Chocolate Coffee Cake
description: Moist chocolate cake infused with coffee flavour and topped with a crumbly chocolate streusel. A rich and indulgent treat.

name: Oreo Brownie Trifle
description: Layers of rich brownies, creamy pudding, whipped cream, and crushed Oreos stacked into a delightful and decadent trifle.
